description: This file declares external function prototypes and macro guards for the ANSC Server Doctor TCP object within the ANSC framework. It includes function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling objects, and initializing the server TCP object, serving as an interface for external modules.

methods.name: AnscCreateServerDoctorTcp
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Server Doctor TCP object with provided context handles.

methods.name: AnscSdtoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Server Doctor (SDTO) object.

methods.name: AnscSdtoRemove
methods.description: Removes the instance of the SDTO object.

methods.name: AnscSdtoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls objects necessary for the SDTO's operation.
